<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1436,402,571]" pageId="12">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,286,402,427]" pageId="12">Etymology.</emphasis>
The species epithet refers to the rich, whitish pubescence giving the cuticular surface a silky appearance.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
